{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423700/extras/About_Section_Banner.png?t=1738433037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is\u00a0PL4no-B</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PL4no-B is a 2D top-down game where the main objective is to have fun with friends. Team up or face off as Red and Blue team. It\u2019s packed with clever strategies and funny moments, but at its heart, it\u2019s all about having a great time together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423700/extras/1.gif?t=1738433037\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Grab Your Gear and Get Ready for Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Whether you\u2019re engaging in a 1v1 death match, a 4v4 detonation battle where you plant and defuse bombs, or trying out other exciting game modes, every match brings something new to the table. With friends by your side, each round is full of laughs and surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your arsenal is packed with a variety of weapons and utilities to fit any play-style. From powerful firearms to quirky gadgets, there's always something new to try.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pistols</strong>: Lightweight and quick, perfect for close encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rifles</strong>: Reliable for medium to long-range combat with steady firepower.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Snipers</strong>: Take the cover and make every shot count.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shotguns</strong>: Close-quarters dominance, delivering massive damage at short range.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Grenades</strong>: Use them strategically to control the battlefield\u2014each with its own unique effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Quirky Weapons</strong>: Experiment with unusual and fun tools to surprise your enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423700/extras/new_gifs2.gif?t=1738433037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The more your play, the better it gets</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize your character appearance</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play through a variety of game modes with your friends</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Earn points and experience through matches</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spend your points to customize your base</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Use your base to unlock new items and expeditions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Invade other people\u2019s bases</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Make more friends</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423700/extras/test.gif?t=1738433037\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Compelling Game Modes to Explore</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Detonation -</strong>\u00a0Play as Red Team and plant a bomb, or as Blue team and try to defuse it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Death Match -</strong>\u00a0The classic showdown\u2014rack up kills and outscore your opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hordes -</strong>\u00a0Join forces to complete missions while battling relentless waves of enemies.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sandbox -</strong>\u00a0Test out weapons, set up custom scenarios, and have fun experimenting with your friends.</p></li></ul><p clas